LVFS Release Notes

1. Write release entries:

git shortlog 1.1.4.. | grep -i -v trivial | grep -v Merge > NEWS.new
add to lvfs/templates/docs-news.html and lvfs/templates/private.html

<div class="card mb-3">
  <div class="card-header card-title list-group-item-info">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col col-lg-8 text-truncate">LVFS Version 1.1.5 Released</div>
      <div class="col">
        <span class="float-right">2019-xx-xx</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <p class="card-text">
      This release adds the following features:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>xyx</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="card-text">This release fixes the following bugs:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>xyx</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

2. Commit changes to git:

# MAKE SURE THIS IS CORRECT
export release_ver="1.1.5"
git commit -a -m "Release LVFS ${release_ver}"
git tag -s -f -m "Release LVFS ${release_ver}" "${release_ver}"
<wait>
git push --tags
git push

3. Do post release version bump in this file

git commit -a -m "trivial: Post release version bump"
git push
